Date: Tue, 11 Feb 2014 15:48:02 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0261/1074] ENGR00298524-5 ARM: dts: imx6sx: Add romcp module

Add ROMCP module and set it as syscon.

Signed-off-by: Anson Huang <b20788@freescale.com>
[Original patch taken from git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git]
Signed-off-by: Biyao Zhai <biyao.zhai@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx.dtsi |    5 +++++
 1 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx.dtsi
index f65abb3..d76c9e9 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx.dtsi
@@ -244,6 +244,11 @@
 				reg = <0x021b0000 0x4000>;
 			};
 
+			romcp@021ac000 {
+				compatible = "fsl,imx6sx-romcp", "syscon";
+				reg = <0x021ac000 0x4000>;
+			};
+
 			tzasc@021d0000 { /* TZASC1 */
 				reg = <0x021d0000 0x4000>;
 				interrupts = <0 108 0x04>;
